---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import PrimaryButton from "../components/PrimaryButton.astro";
import SecondaryButton from "../components/SecondaryButton.astro";
import { sitePath } from "../lib/urls";
---
<BaseLayout title="页面未找到" description="你访问的纤云叙官网页面不存在。" noindex>
  <section class="page-hero"><div class="shell"><p class="eyebrow">404</p><h1>这段路径没有落成页面。</h1><p>链接可能已变化，或者地址输入有误。可以回到首页，也可以直接查看当前 macOS Beta 下载。</p><div class="button-row" style="margin-top: var(--space-6)"><PrimaryButton href={sitePath("/")}>返回首页</PrimaryButton><SecondaryButton href={sitePath("/download/")}>前往下载</SecondaryButton></div></div></section>
</BaseLayout>
